body_html:
Thank you all for this discussion. This matched my exact scenario as well. Worked on Window GPU TF but failed on Linux CPU TF build. I found some None type objects from my sequencing algorithms in my input array (an array representing ASCII characters). A sample of one of my failing array vectors looked like:

[34 51 90 26 9 31 40 72 78 77 46 92 19 None 73 45 None 93 14 16]
